headline.main: In Past Land Cases, Gorsuch Has Limited Environmentalists
headline.print_headline: In Past Land Cases, Gorsuch Has Limited Environmentalists

lead_paragraph: Deepening the crisis among France's conservatives, former French Prime Minister Alain Juppe firmly declined Monday to step into the country's presidential race to rescue his party's chances in the event that embattled candidate Francois Fillon withdraws.
